=========
ArxivNotificator
=========

ArxivNotificator -- is a little script that notify users about interesting articles in ArXiv.org by e-mail. The papers are chosen by key-words in title and in abstract and by authors.

============
Usage
============

Fill in fields in settings.py:
    server -- mail server name.
    port -- port number
    sender -- sender name
    passw -- password of sender
    recipient -- recipient name
    keywords -- list of interesting key-words
    keyauthors -- list of interesting authors